    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>众神带走了你的女儿。为了拯救她，你必须成为一个怪物——不背叛你的人民。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039230/extras/d5bc6a48b9153336d4f53236c6e0729a.poster.avif?t=1770322240\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039230/extras/d5bc6a48b9153336d4f53236c6e0729a.webm?t=1770322240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039230/extras/d5bc6a48b9153336d4f53236c6e0729a.mp4?t=1770322240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在发现禁忌之石的世界中，四位古老的神祇降临人类，带来毁灭。在混乱中，一位父亲的生活被摧毁，当他的女儿被带走——消失在神圣的未知中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但这不是一个英雄的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个绝望、责任...和复仇的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一个高贵的领主—被赋予保护你濒临死亡的王国的任务—现在被迫踏上穿越神话之地的危险征途去拯救你的女儿。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一步都模糊了救世主与罪人的界限，每一个你面对的神都把你带得更近真相...或是彻底的毁灭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039230/extras/19cfb51a23b64162ab75da8e38e000a2.poster.avif?t=1770322240\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039230/extras/19cfb51a23b64162ab75da8e38e000a2.webm?t=1770322240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039230/extras/19cfb51a23b64162ab75da8e38e000a2.mp4?t=1770322240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>潜行与砍杀战斗的结合</strong><br>悄无声息地消灭敌人——或以高速、动漫风格的动作将它们切割开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>深入的角色成长与神器升级</strong><br>解锁技能，并根据你的路径发展你的战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解谜与探索</strong><br>发现失落的文明、古老的符文和禁忌的知识。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039230/extras/627f815d069e827ec14624be8059b816.poster.avif?t=1770322240\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039230/extras/627f815d069e827ec14624be8059b816.webm?t=1770322240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039230/extras/627f815d069e827ec14624be8059b816.mp4?t=1770322240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>故事驱动的RPG体验</strong><br>做出影响你的人们、你女儿的命运和你自己灵魂的重要选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>富有氛围的动漫视觉和戏剧性的过场动画</strong><br>从阴暗的森林到废墟中的神殿，每个区域都讲述着一个故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在Excoverse中，你的旅程不仅仅是一次救援任务——它是一场审判。<br>你会揭开神的真实意图，重聚你的家人... 还是会变成你最害怕的那个人？ </p>",
